<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="price-n">price <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /praɪs/    美 /praɪs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>价格；价钱：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>at a <strong>high / low price</strong> 
以高/低价</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>代价；牺牲：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We <strong>paid a</strong> heavy <strong>price</strong> for the victory. 
我们为胜利付出了沉重的代价。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="at-the-price-of">at the price of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>以…的代价：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She achieved success at the price of her health.
她的成功是以牺牲自身健康为代价的。</p></div></div>